title: State Bar of Texas Annual Meet
creator: CrowdCompass Inc

extendedInfo.description: Join us for the 2012 State Bar of Texas Annual Meeting, June 14 and 15 in Houston. For one low registration price you will receive two full days of CLE that will educate, motivate, and inspire. From sessions on law practice management to ethics to legislative updates, there is something for the first year associate to the seasoned professional. Register today at www.texasbar.com/annualmeeting. Use our SBOT12 mobile app now to browse sessions and plan your schedule before you arrive in Houston.
